Which of the following is **NOT** a problem with the accessibility of the following code?

```
<p>The <a href="syllabus.html" tabindex="1">syllabus</a> has all the information you need.</p>
<style>
p {color:#000000; background-color:#4DB396; font-size:1em}
a {color:#6A2C3E}
a:hover, a:active, a:focus { outline: none; border: 0; }
</style>
```

See the code in JSBin
